title: 2019 Week 9 Spooky Preview
itunes:title: 2019 Week 9 Spooky Preview
description:
A room filled with spooky guys - Damned Hangedzuz, Crypt Wesselthing, Darc Sesslair, and Grehgg Risenghoul preview each of the upcoming games of Week 9 on this spooky Halloween including the Browns Broncos ( 15:53), the Lions Raiders matchup (29:03) and if the Patriots will stay undefeated against the Ravens (57:40)
